We used a binomial model with a log link to estimate the RR of predischarge mortality with longer cooling, deeper cooling, or both, compared with standard cooling. We included the main effects of duration and depth of cooling and the interaction term to assess its magnitude. Letting yi be the outcome of predischarge death (1 = yes, 0 = no), the model is expressed as:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
